{"tid":1012572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"火辣女模「3點貼膠帶」買得來速　男店員緊盯巨乳看傻","createTime":"2019-02-07T16:29:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-08T09:48:52.000Z","uid":212399,"like":27,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"3ef1c39fc3c8746bff2a6c9d6ee16aa9865f5beb","tid":1012572,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T16:29:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3777/d3777978.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3777%2Fd3777978.jpg&h=6b4bb883&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲女子出門居然身上只貼膠帶。（圖／翻攝自YouTube／PlayHouse TV）<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n美國一名麥當勞店員在得來速工作時，一輛開著法拉利的客人來點餐，車窗搖下後，裡面竟然坐著一名全身只用膠帶遮住3點的性感女模，嚇得他整個人呆住。這支獵奇影片分享在YouTube上後，立即吸引20多萬人點閱，許多網友大讚「我忍不住看了5次」、「我超愛，她太棒了」。<br />\n這支影片去年12月14日分享在YouTube頻道「PlayHouse TV」，影片中，來自邁阿密的性感女模阿曼達(Amanda Trivizas)，和頻道主傑伊(Jay Tabiza)一同到麥當勞點餐，但她的身上居然沒有穿任何的衣服，只用膠帶遮住3點，大方秀出她前凸後翹的好身材。<br />\n男店員看到阿曼達的驚人打扮，整個人當場嚇傻，但仍敬業收好了錢，雙眼也緊盯著火辣身材，沒有錯過讓眼睛大吃冰淇淋的好機會，而當阿曼達前往第二個窗口取餐時，送餐的女店員反應雖然淡定許多，但也忍不住多看了她幾眼。<br />\n▼女子的好身材，讓店員看傻了眼。（圖／翻攝自YouTube／PlayHouse TV）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3777/d3777979.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3777%2Fd3777979.jpg&h=a7e1b81d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/HvrhBRF9BlA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHvrhBRF9BlA&d=HNFwsad0YdNlvWXbC%2BF%2BcnjCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=200823dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/HvrhBRF9BlA</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190207/1336258.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190207%2F1336258.htm&d=HNFwsad0YdNlvWXbC%2BF%2BcnjCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=28d3cc4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190207/1336258.htm</a>"},{"pid":"49845d4fca3b733dad490d01d641d620bb0381d3","tid":1012572,"uid":33059,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":